ure patterns:\n+- **No tests for `GET /world/entities` — severity: blocking.** The acceptance criterion is not exercised. A `tests/test_narrative_api_entities.py` covering at minimum: (a) `domain=deniable` returns only deniable+shared; (b) no domain defaults to shared; (c) `type` filter; (d) pagination (`limit`, `offset`) must be added before this task is considered done.\n+- **Pagination may underdeliver under native-paginating stores — severity: minor.** If the backing store honours `limit`/`offset` natively but ignores `domain_filter`, post-filtering silently returns fewer than `limit` items per page. Consider fetching with a multiplier or delegating full pagination responsibility to the store.\n+- `domain=deniable` → only entities with `domain in {\"deniable\", \"shared\"}` returned.\n+- No `domain` param → only `domain=\"shared\"` entities returned.\n+- `type=character` filter narrows results.\n+\n+### verify.md v004 (created)\n+\n+- Candidate path: `sdp/templates/candidates/verify/v004.md`\n+- Rationale: Auto-generated candidate for verify.md from the latest 20 retry-context entries. Recurring failure patterns:\n+- **No tests for `GET /world/entities` — severity: blocking.** The acceptance criterion is not exercised. A `tests/test_narrative_api_entities.py` covering at minimum: (a) `domain=deniable` returns only deniable+shared; (b) no domain defaults to shared; (c) `type` filter; (d) pagination (`limit`, `offset`) must be added before this task is considered done.\n+- **Pagination may underdeliver under native-paginating stores — severity: minor.** If the backing store honours `limit`/`offset` natively but ignores `domain_filter`, post-filtering silently returns fewer than `limit` items per page. Consider fetching with a multiplier or delegating full pagination responsibility to the store.\n+- `domain=deniable` → only entities with `domain in {\"deniable\", \"shared\"}` returned.\n+- No `domain` param → only `domain=\"shared\"` entities returned.\n+- `type=ch