ccompanying tests in `tests/test_smoke_narrative_script.py` and `tests/test_narrative_api_entities.py` provide solid regression coverage. Specifically, the \"underdelivery\" risk in pagination is addressed in the code by fetching with a multiplier.\n\n## Issues Found\nNone.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe documentation correctly reflects the choice to use `/health` (aligning with the actual API) rather than `/healthz`/`/readyz` (which was a previous contract mismatch). The dual header support in the script ensures compatibility with different auth enforcement modes.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-016 @20260502t001347zc-verify.md"}}
